column6: MATCH (s1:Station)<-[:`途径`]-(id1:TrainNode)<-[:`站点信息`]-(no:TrainNo)-[:`站点信息`]->(id2:TrainNode)-[:`途径`]->(s2:Station) WHERE s1.name='广州东站' AND s2.name='上海站' AND no.name=~'Z\\d{1,4}' WITH id1,no,id2 MATCH (id1)-[:`站点顺序`]->(seq1:TrainInfo),(id2)-[:`站点顺序`]->(seq2:TrainInfo) WHERE toInt(seq1.name) < toInt(seq2.name) RETURN no.name AS train_no
